WHAT IF THE CUSTOMER HAS AN ONGOING PROMO, WILL THE PROMO REMAIN ACTIVE?

YES!
If the customer (with TP 20GB or 80GB) has an ongoing promo (for example the -5€ for life promo), he will keep it!

Also in case of a tariff change, the customer keeps his promo!
(Except if the customer has the Double data promo, he will lose the promo in case of a tariff change)


